25
00:01:28,510 --> 00:01:32,060
You need to use separate keys because otherwise,

26
00:01:32,060 --> 00:01:37,550
the coins in cold storage will be vulnerable if the hot storage is compromised.

27
00:01:37,550 --> 00:01:40,840
You need to use separate keys because otherwise,

28
00:01:40,840 --> 00:01:46,280
the coins in a cold storage will be vulnerable if the hot storage is compromised.

29
00:01:46,280 --> 00:01:51,490
